lead_paragraph: Misfiring Manchester United must show some fighting spirit against third-tier Shrewsbury Town in the FA Cup on Monday night if they want to avoid a second successive season without a trophy, defender Chris Smalling has said.

headline.print_headline: Smalling Wants United to Show Fight at Shrewsbury
headline.main: Smalling Wants United to Show Fight at Shrewsbury
